OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,FConservative MP Greg Smith, Lib Dem MP
OL,8,FVikki Slade and Labour MP Kevin
OL,9,FMcKenna discuss their parties'
OL,10,Fprospects at the local elections on
OL,11,FITV's The Last Word
OL,13,FThe local election results will not be
OL,14,F"spectacular" for Labour, the
OL,15,FConservatives or the Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats, a Tory MP has predicted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
