OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,FMid Buckinghamshire MP Greg Smith said
OL,8,Fthe Conservatives were "fighting for
OL,9,Fevery single vote" in a system where
OL,10,Fsupport was now being "split across
OL,11,Ffive different parties".
OL,13,FThe Tories are defending majorities on
OL,14,Fcounty councils in Sussex and
OL,15,FHampshire which last had a full set of
OL,16,Flocal elections in 2021.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
