PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776453069
OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,F"We're coming off quite a high base,
OL,8,Fbut we are out there under new
OL,9,Fleadership... setting out a positive
OL,10,Fmessage to win Conservative
OL,11,Fcouncillors", Mr Smith told ITV's The
OL,12,FLast Word.
OL,14,FOn 7 May, Labour is battling to retain
OL,15,Fcontrol of a handful of unitary,
OL,16,Fdistrict and borough councils across
OL,17,Fthe South of England.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
