PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776453069
OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,FLabour MP Kevin McKenna said his party
OL,8,Fwas "fighting very hard across the
OL,9,Fregion" and argued there were "huge
OL,10,Fopportunities" for councils to "really
OL,11,Frebalance local economies".
OL,13,FThe Liberal Democrats are expecting to
OL,14,Fgain seats and could take control of
OL,15,Fsome councils in the region, according
OL,16,Fto the party's former local government
OL,17,Fspokesperson.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
