PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776453069
OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,FMid Dorset and North Poole MP, Vikki
OL,8,FSlade, told ITV Meridian's monthly
OL,9,Fpolitical programme: "I think there's
OL,10,Fa chance of gaining (control of) a
OL,11,Fcouple more, gaining (seats) across
OL,12,Flots of councils, particularly as we
OL,13,Fhad such good results at the general
OL,14,Felection.
OL,16,F"We've now got MPs in areas we didn't
OL,17,Fhave before, which shows how you can
OL,18,Factually make a difference."
