OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,FGreen leader Zack Polanski said his
OL,8,Fparty "should be making significant
OL,9,Fgains" in "places like East Sussex...
OL,10,Fwhere we've started to do really well."
OL,12,FOn a visit to Forest Row near East
OL,13,FGrinstead, this week, Mr Polanski
OL,14,Fadded: "What the Green Party is
OL,15,Fpresenting right across the South East
OL,16,Fis a politics of hope."
OL,18,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage said
OL,19,Fsuccess for his party would be
OL,20,F"winning lots of seats and winning
OL,21,Flots of councils".
