OL,3,CLocal elections 'won't be spectacular'
OL,4,Cfor traditional parties, Tory MP
OL,5,Cpredicts
OL,7,F"I can't put a number on it, Mr Farage
OL,8,Fadded. "All I can tell you is we are
OL,9,Ftrying our absolute hardest."
OL,11,FITV Meridian's monthly political
OL,12,Fprogramme, The Last Word, is on ITV1
OL,13,Fat 11.20pm on Thursday, 16 April 2026.
OL,14,FWatch the full episode below or on
OL,15,FITVX and YouTube
